    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Non-Response Bias</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Bias that occurs when people from certain groups opt-out of surveys at different rates than users from other groups. This is also called as Participation bias</skos:definition>
