    <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Potential RiskSource</skos:prefLabel>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Indicates a concept can potentially be a 'risk source' concept within an use-case</skos:definition>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/dpv#RiskConcept"/>
    <skos:broader rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/dpv#RiskConcept"/>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A concept being an instance of PotentialRiskSource is a suggestion that the concept can be a 'risk' within an use-case - this suggestion is not exclusive and the concept may also be instances of other potential concepts to indicate the multiple possible roles a concept can take. This suggestion can be ignored if it is not applicable to the use-case</skos:scopeNote>
    <dct:created rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2024-09-29</dct:created>
